headline: DoorDash offers fulfillment service for retailers
summary: DoorDash on Tuesday unveiled a fulfillment service for retailers, a road-capable delivery robot, an autonomous delivery platform and a smart-scale device to ensure order accuracy. The post DoorDash offers fulfillment service for retailers appeared first on FreightWaves.

headline: Countree Food Takes Key Role at World Processed Deciduous Fruit Conference (CANCON16)
summary: QINGDAO, China, Oct. 01, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- The 16th World Processed Deciduous Fruit Conference (CANCON16), the largest and most influential international event for the canned fruit industry, recently concluded with discussions on the future challenges and innovations shaping the sector. The conference drew industry leaders, processors, and growers from major producing nations like the USA, Chile, Argentina, South Africa, and various European countries. headline: GoodRx Launches Brand Medication Savings Program at National Retail Pharmacy
summary: SANTA MONICA, Calif., October 01, 2025--GoodRx (Nasdaq: GDRX), the leading platform for medication savings in the U.S., today announced the availability of its brand medication savings solution, RxSmartSaver powered by GoodRx, at Kroger pharmacies nationwide. RxSmartSaver brings medication affordability directly to the pharmacy counter, improving the patient experience while delivering stronger economics for the retail partner.
